{
  "texts": [
    "Shukla et al.",
    "reported a deep-learning model to predict DDIs (Shukla et al. 2020).",
    "Their model is built by integrating CNNs, recurrent neural networks, and mixture density networks.",
    "It has an accuracy of 98.50 ± 0.6%.",
    "Schwarz et al. reported an Explainable AI (XAI) model called 'AttentionDDI' for DDI predictions."
  ]
}